And from Jerusalem, and from Edom, and from the borders of Jordan. And those who were around Beersheba and Sidon, a very great multitude, when they heard how it was done, came unto him.
He told his disciples to follow him in a small ship for the purpose of the gathering, so that they would not bother him.
Because he had healed many, so that a diseased person came to him, longing to touch him.
And the foul spirits, when their gaze darted towards him, screamed, saying, “You are the son of God!”
