Then he ascended the mountain and called those whom he wanted, and they went unto him.
And He appointed twelve, and sent them out to Him, saying, “Go and preach.”
And they will have dominion over healing the illnesses and driving out devils.
And he gave to Simon the name Peter, which means Rock.
Jacob ben Zbad and John, Jacob’s brother, and for them they gave the name Buanarges, which is to say, son of thunder.
