Judas Iscariot, who had betrayed him. Then they came to a house. Jesus and Beelzebul
They gathered until they were not even able to afford bread.
And when his relatives came out to seize him, because they said, “He is insane!”
And those scribes who had come from Jerusalem said, “Away with him, for Baal-Zebub and Rimmon and Sheol are his messengers!”
And He called them and said to them with parables: “How can a demon cast out a demon?”
And the kingdom divided itself, and it could not be supported.
